-= Translations =-
Create/update translation template:
    python i18n.py -p

Create/update compiled mo languages:
    python i18n.py -m


-= Install build system =-
Windows:
    Install Python 2.7:
        https://www.python.org/downloads/windows/
    Install py2exe:
        https://sourceforge.net/projects/py2exe/files/py2exe/0.6.9/py2exe-0.6.9.win32-py2.7.exe/download
    Install PyGTK AIO:
        http://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/binaries/win32/pygtk/2.24/pygtk-all-in-one-2.24.2.win32-py2.7.msi
    Install GTK2 Themes:
        https://sourceforge.net/projects/gtk-win/files/GTK%2B%20Themes%20Package/2009-09-07/gtk2-themes-2009-09-07-ash.exe/download
    Install Inno Setup QuickStart Pack:
        http://www.jrsoftware.org/isdl.php

macOS:
    wget https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/gtk-osx/raw/master/gtk-osx-setup.sh
    sh gtk-osx-setup.sh
    cp mac/jhbuildrc-custom ~/.config/jhbuildrc-custom
    cp mac/pigeonplanner.modules ~/.config/pigeonplanner.modules
    jhbuild bootstrap-gtk-osx
    jhbuild build
    jhbuild shell
    python3 -m pip install -r requirements.txt


-= Packaging =-
Linux:
    python setup.py sdist

Windows:
    python setup.py py2exe
    python win/build_packages.py

macOS:
    jhbuild shell
    python3 -m pip install .
    python3 mac/build_package.py


-= Other =-
    export PYTHONPATH=dev
    python setup.py develop --install-dir dev

